{"tid":994273,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[1月新番] 粉彩回憶 / ぱすてるメモリーズ","createTime":"2019-01-24T14:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T15:36:34.000Z","uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7a73f51a8484ee82c1eeabe68b99a4924395f1df","tid":994273,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T14:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hXQgtRV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhXQgtRV.jpg&h=57cde250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n監督：篠崎康行<br />\n系列構成：玉井☆豪<br />\n角色原案：ナシキネロ<br />\n角色設計：瀨川真矢<br />\n美術監督：葛琳<br />\n音響監督：今泉雄一<br />\n音樂：立山秋航<br />\n音樂製作：MAGES.<br />\n動畫製作：project No.9<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n浅木泉水：新田ひより<br />\n榊亜矢香：鳥部万里子<br />\nイリーナ・レスコヴァ：内山夕実<br />\n二条院薫子：藤井ゆきよ<br />\n町屋結衣奈：村川梨衣<br />\n江戸川橋美智：大空直美<br />\n千住南海：山本亜衣<br />\n舞子ちまり：小倉唯<br />\n目白渚央：花守ゆみり<br />\n来島怜：久保ユリカ<br />\n里中小町：戸田めぐみ<br />\n六郷沙織：小岩井ことり<br />\nねじれウサギ：森永千才<br />\n摩耶：たかはし智秋<br />\n<br />\n公式：<a href=\"https://pasumemotv.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpasumemotv.com%2F&d=dtASCCMpoeTeRctmJjOlvbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f1885142\" target=\"_blank\">https://pasumemotv.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n本作是一款以秋葉原為舞台的遊戲，時代設定在距今不久的未來20XX 年。雖然秋葉原曾經被稱作禦宅聖地，但是在20XX年時、當地的宅文化卻整個沒落。玩家將扮演殘存在秋葉原中的少數宅店店長，與店裡身負各種宅能力的女孩們同心協力，奪回人們心中被奪走的回憶而與神秘敵人展開戰鬥。"},{"pid":"2f492d28a090abd50a37a1b6dcd2afd868e3004d","tid":994273,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"呢套應該無咩人會睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢咁樣向點兔「致敬」法，會唔會被芳文社屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cfc1e4fae9c12524d22bab2671889544459f66e","tid":994273,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"うさぎ變左うなぎ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161517d7ebd355cbbc10e46bbeb271e784821d1c","tid":994273,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:51:59.000Z","msg":"其實套野除左作畫真係差少少之外<br />\n自己都覺得OK既<br />\nSell 對作品既情懷<br />\n每集都穿越去果個作品既世界入面<br />\n如果鍾意相關作品既話<br />\n睇落去都會幾有共鳴"},{"pid":"12653815102a1dd09f86489d9f6ef2e2d2ce5a89","tid":994273,"uid":195124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f492d28a090abd50a37a1b6dcd2afd868e3004d","tid":994273,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"呢套應該無咩人會睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢咁樣向點兔「致敬」法，會唔會被芳文社屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:01:53.000Z","msg":"呢套無咩人睇既大冷門，我已經追到第3話了~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a395b7be77c4d2202d29cfbbb170535f3a6d6d","tid":994273,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12653815102a1dd09f86489d9f6ef2e2d2ce5a89","tid":994273,"uid":195124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f492d28a090abd50a37a1b6dcd2afd868e3004d","tid":994273,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T14: